column3: Level 1 and entry level qualifications: 1 to 4 GCSEs grade A* to C, Basic or Essential Skills
column4: Level 2 qualifcations: School Certification, 5 or more GCSEs (A* to C or 9 to 4) or equivalent.
column5: Level 3 qualifications: 2 or more A levels or equivalent
column6: Level 4 qualifications or above: degree (BA, BSc), higher degree (MA, PhD, PGCE))
